Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样?不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩，厉害\N是宝石吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到彩虹似的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是魔法石也不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.58,0:01:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能还有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?    恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石降下后30年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类那不屈的生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次引导人们\N去建立一个新城市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但旧的地区\N现在仍是不幸的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负着可怕的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还留下一些废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和先进的米加罗城市相比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是处对比很强烈的地区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是斜坡，真累
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何会凹凸不平?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陨石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是30年前陨石的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿你连这些也不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿你对以前的事\N不感兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，看，是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55\fad(200,200)\pos(480,680)}力量最强!钢铁战士出场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷电不行，振作点!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再继续操控下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢脸，你已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在难以立足的地方战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用道路雷电是很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N也可说是某人驾驶得差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我那车子比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且雷电的机能也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水面也能走得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管电单车的性能有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管换驾驶的人也会是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛，放手...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找死吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是由我说才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因你们常这么孩子气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以学生才当你们是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，放手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才应该放手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我放手\N也不能保证你会放手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个比你更加值得信任的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了世界，为了人们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以双手把你干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.69,0:05:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢铁战士，测试开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美梦妮吧，什么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想对我们做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样?有意思跟他交手吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美梦妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这么不怕死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达奥罗斯，还差一点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙拿曼达，别着急\N快可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快可以和这达奥罗斯合体了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看，是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走进这样的地方吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心脚下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我好等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是猛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍\N这两位是我的朋友猛和裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会为我们带路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带了女孩子来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉和真儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一，你带了额外的电筒来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:09:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我一个，我想给他们   恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向中间弯曲一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在里面的药物起了反应\N而射出光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一，怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西向着这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，逃吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古尼城的地下街?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如发生什么事便麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想告密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是认为告诉老师会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻宝?蠢材!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享，为何你不一起去?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻宝好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等...我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该更像老师一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们比其他人更担心大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不老实而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是变得像老师吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，好像已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怪物火车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎会的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱童快出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去的话，可能再来也不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚走，怎会马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点，我快不能呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是还好好地在呼吸吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有那样的东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是初次见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幽灵火车呀，不会有错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会有错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?有入侵者?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达奥罗斯不久便会苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可让他们接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美梦妮，肯定吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 不会有错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你们的下面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是旧地下铁的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有强烈的妖魔反应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以红外线去找小孩们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却找到妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美梦妮\N小孩们也好像到了地下洞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚的看到脚印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵，也许现在正和妖魔在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说笑啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如不在被妖魔发现之前找到小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美梦妮，这里用不到\N我的车子和亮的电单车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可否使用刚才的钢铁战士?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好提议!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白，立即传送过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK，传送完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传送超音护甲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Borg Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷电拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了，快去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积克，退后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉，喝咖啡吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是即溶的，真儿也喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛，你们在这里生活吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能，我们住在地面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是处很大的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有上吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一也是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用上学也行\N现在也十分快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...父母在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人也在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很晚才会回来，猛的家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小孩完全不关心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不觉得寂寞吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一你在白天一直是独个儿吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有猛和其他朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物方面怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天要独个儿去弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再谈这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像莫莉你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多事情是不会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛他们喜欢这样的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对普通人来说是不能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱童你能明白吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给，咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢\N-真儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉，谢谢你替我们担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们有很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没想过什么辛苦或寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比下\N莫莉你一生不会知道的事、
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体验到的事，我们却能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能到学校去也不会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且能为莫莉他们在这里带路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是裕一，了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我老是在乱问些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用介怀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已习惯了被人这样的去问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一，是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是初遇见乱童的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也老是在问这些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且态度很糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，相比之下\N莫莉还是蛮可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-听到一些声音\N-哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是幽灵火车吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么地方也好\N你们躲起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快点\N-超音战士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想是谁，原来是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这里变为你们的墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你蟑螂似的在洞穴四处出没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用子弹来代替杀虫剂孝敬你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达奥罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟沙拿这合体吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积克，别大意，来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看三重怪兽沙拿曼达的英姿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，小孩们呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下面的地下街躲起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙拿曼达，收拾他们!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉他们的寻宝之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽发生意想不到的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但莫莉他们找到\N比宝物更好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:48.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
